    ],
    [
      1,
      "p",
      [
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
          "While the car's first owner didn't drive it much, we can't say that we would have the same restraint. Every time we've had an opportunity to slide "
        ],
        [
          0,
          [
            0
          ],
          1,
          "behind the wheel"
        ],
        [
          0,
          [],
          0,
